Problem: Power of Two
Topic: Bit Manipulation, Math
Difficulty: Easy

Approach:
Repeatedly divide the number by 2 while it is divisible. If the final value becomes 1, it is a power of two; otherwise, it is not.

Time Complexity: O(log n)
Space Complexity: O(1)

Code:
class Solution {
public:
    bool isPowerOfTwo(int n) {
        if(n==0){
            return false;
        }
        while(n%2==0){
            n=n/2;
        }
        if(n==1){
            return true;
        }
        return false;
    }
};
